header.gameNote: BIG WEST MEN'S TOURNAMENT - QUARTERFINALS AT ANAHEIM CA

article.headline: UC Davis 68, Cal St.-Fullerton 65
article.story: ANAHEIM, Calif. -- Joe Harden had 20 points and nine rebounds to lead UC Davis to a 68-65 victory over Cal State Fullerton in the second round of the Big West Conference tournament Thursday night. Ryan Howley added 14 points off the bench for the fourth-seeded Aggies (14-17), who will play top-seeded UC Santa Barbara (18-9) in the semifinals Friday night. Dominic Calegari had 13 points, six rebounds and four assists. Gerard Anderson had 17 points, five rebounds and five assists for the fifth-seeded Titans (16-15). Jer'Vaughn Johnson added 15 points.
